txt.en: Defeat many enemies in the Wildwood.
Many more Orc-kind have fallen before you. The Free Peoples in the Wildwood are grateful for your aid.
Many cruel and greedy Men have met their match against you. The Free Peoples in the Wildwood are grateful for your aid.
You have assisted those in the Wildwood, facing the many threats and challenges that plague these lands.
You have become known as an exceptional hunter among those in the Wildwood.
Defeat many enemies in the Wildwood.
